    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s been such a dependable car for me, and I just know you\u2019re going to love how it handles. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself! You won't be disappointed!",
