    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit retains its high-revving character with crisp throttle response via factory individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, directing power through a functional M-variable differential lock. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings, preserving the chassis's balanced 50/50 weight distribution. A well-sorted example ready for spirited driving.",
      "price": 34800.0,
