    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of reliability and style, maintained with a meticulous eye for detail. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, showing only the minor, superficial marks consistent with careful road use. Step inside to a cabin that feels fresh and inviting; the premium upholstery is free of tears or significant wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the intuitive navigation\u2014functions perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and performs with quiet strength, benefiting from a history of timely oil changes and preventative maintenance. The transmission is crisp and responsive, providing a smooth ride whether you're navigating city streets or cruising the highway. The tires offer excellent grip with plenty of life left, and the suspension remains firm and quiet. This car comes with a complete set of service records and a clean title, offering peace of mind to its next owner. It is a solid, dependable vehicle that looks and drives beautifully.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
