    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, an exemplary choice for those seeking performance and reliability. This unit has been subjected to a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring that all mechanical systems operate at peak efficiency. Both the exterior and interior have been preserved to a high standard, reflecting a history of diligent care and professional upkeep. This vehicle represents a sophisticated investment for the discerning motorist, offering a turnkey driving experience without compromise.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
