    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next big adventure without any fuss. It drives smoothly and has plenty of life left in it! If you're looking for something reliable and fun to drive, this is the one for you. Drop me a message\u2014I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
