      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The mechanical integrity of this chassis is prioritized, with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul already completed to ensure variable valve timing precision. Power is delivered through the factory M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional lateral grip and exit speeds. The suspension maintains its signature McPherson strut/multi-link geometry with refreshed bushings for tactile steering feedback. While the aesthetic shows light patina, the powertrain is tuned to factory tolerances, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience.",
